cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.IR 

This paper proposes a method for learning data selection measures for transfer learning, which is a topic that falls under the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), natural language processing (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), and information retrieval (cs.IR). Given that the paper focuses on evaluating the proposed method on tasks related to sentiment analysis, part-of-speech tagging, and parsing, it is likely to be classified under one or more of these sub-categories.
